<div class="large-12 columns">

	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-11 large-centered columns" style="box-shadow: 0 0 20px #444">
			<% if @charity == nil %>
				<div style="width: 100%; height: 250px; background-image: url(/assets/placeholder.jpg); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: 100%">
				</div>
			<% else %>
				<%= image_tag(@charity.header_image.to_s) %>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 30px;">
		<div class="large-5 columns" style="padding: 10px 15px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #666; border: solid 1px #555; text-align: justify; margin-left: 20px;">
			<p><b>This is where the static info goes.</b><br> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla a nisi vel justo laoreet suscipit. Cras molestie sapien ligula, ut consectetur sapien scelerisque non. Mauris ornare vestibulum tempor. Donec sit amet enim suscipit, pulvinar orci id, vestibulum eros. Maecenas ac diam rhoncus quam tincidunt auctor. Suspendisse et odio vitae erat volutpat dapibus ut aliquet tortor. Mauris pellentesque, arcu eget pharetra porttitor, purus dui tristique velit, in lobortis libero nibh quis nisl. Cras gravida ipsum eget est sodales, non tristique tortor pellentesque. Nulla tellus sem, rutrum et placerat eget, congue id ipsum.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-6 columns right" style="padding: 10px 15px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #666; border: solid 1px #555; text-align: justify; margin-right: 20px;">
			<% if @charity == nil %>
				<h4 style="margin-top:0">Title Goes Here</h4>
				<p><b>And Text goes here</b><br>Suspendisse et odio vitae erat volutpat dapibus ut aliquet tortor. Mauris pellentesque, arcu eget pharetra porttitor, purus dui tristique velit, in lobortis libero nibh quis nisl. Cras gravida ipsum eget est sodales, non tristique tortor pellentesque. Nulla tellus sem, rutrum et placerat eget, congue id ipsum.</p>
			<% else %>
				<h4 style="margin-top:0"><%= @charity.title %></h4>

				<p><%= @charity.text %></p>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 45px;">
		<div class="large-3 large-centered columns">
			<% if @charity == nil %>
				<%= link_to 'Set Up Charity of the Month', new_charity_of_the_month_path, class: "button radius expand" %>
			<% else %>
				<%= link_to 'Edit Charity of the Month', edit_charity_of_the_month_path(@charity), class: "button radius expand" %>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 40px;">
		<div class="large-10 columns large-centered" style="border:solid #2B1903 2px; padding: 10px 15px; box-shadow: 0 0 30px #2B1903;">
			<h3 style="text-align:center; margin:0 0 10px 0">Upcomming Events</h3>
			<div class="row">
				<% @events.each do |e| %>
					<% if e.link_url == "" %>

					    <div class="large-6 columns" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
					      <div data-tooltip class="large-11 columns large-centered event_box tip-top" title="No Link Given" style="padding: 10px;">
					        <div class="row">
					          <div class="large-12 columns"><h4 style="text-align:center; margin:-5px 0 2px 0;"><%= e.name %></h4></div>
					        </div>
					        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
					          <div class="large-6 columns" style="text-align:center"><b>Date: </b><%= e.date.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %></div>
					          <div class="large-6 columns" style="text-align:center"><b>Time: </b><%= e.time.strftime("%l:%M %p") %></div>
					        </div>
					        <% unless e.description == "" %>
					          <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
					            <div class="large-12 columns"><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-style: italic"><%= e.description %></p></div>
					          </div>
					        <% end %>
					        <% unless e.street == "" || e.city == "" %>
					          <div class="row">
					            <div class="large-12 columns"><p style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><%= e.street %><br><%= e.city %>, <%= e.state %> <%= e.zip_code %></p></div>
					          </div>
					        <% end %>
					      </div>
					    </div>

					<% else %>
					  <a class="event" href=<%= e.link_url.to_s %>>
					    <div class="large-6 columns" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
					      <div data-tooltip class="large-11 columns large-centered event_box tip-top" title="Link: <%= e.link_url %>" style="padding: 10px;">
					        <div class="row">
					          <div class="large-12 columns"><h4 style="text-align:center; margin:-5px 0 2px 0;"><%= e.name %></h4></div>
					        </div>
					        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
					          <div class="large-6 columns" style="text-align:center"><b>Date: </b><%= e.date.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %></div>
					          <div class="large-6 columns" style="text-align:center"><b>Time: </b><%= e.time.strftime("%l:%M %p") %></div>
					        </div>
					        <% unless e.description == "" %>
					          <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
					            <div class="large-12 columns"><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-style: italic"><%= e.description %></p></div>
					          </div>
					        <% end %>
					        <% unless e.street == "" || e.city == "" %>
					          <div class="row">
					            <div class="large-12 columns"><p style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><%= e.street %><br><%= e.city %>, <%= e.state %> <%= e.zip_code %></p></div>
					          </div>
					        <% end %>
					      </div>
					    </div>
					  </a>





					<% end %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
			<div class="row", style="margin-top: 30px;">
		      <div class="large-7 large-centered columns"> 
		        <div class="large-5 columns left">   
		          <%= link_to 'Edit Events', events_path, class: "button radius expand alert" %>
		        </div>
		        <div class="large-5 columns right">      
		          <%= link_to "New Event", new_event_path, class: "button radius expand" %>
		        </div>
		      </div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


</div>